# Profile Images Directory

This directory should contain your professional photos.

## Recommended Image Specifications:
- Format: WebP (with JPG fallback)
- Dimensions: 400x400px (square aspect ratio)
- File size: < 100KB for optimal loading
- Naming: profile-photo.jpg

## Image Requirements:
- Professional headshot or portrait
- High quality and well-lit
- Appropriate for professional use
- Square crop works best for the circular display

## Optimization Tips:
- Use tools like ImageOptim, TinyPNG, or Squoosh.app
- Consider using WebP format for better compression
- Ensure the image looks good when cropped to a circle